name: Cube Eater (IcicleCom)
description:
Cube Eater V. 0.0.1

This is the final version of the game as of now as this game was made hastily for Dani's (YouTube Content Creator) Basement Game Jam.

Disclaimers:

  • Pause Menu will make you restart.
  • There is only 4 levels as of now.
  • Continued development is undecided.
  • This is my first game jam, so the graphics, design, and code in general may not be 10/10. I did not enter this to win, I entered for a challenge knowing there wasn't a prize. I just started with Unity this year so expect a lot of glitches and bugs. I hope you guys enjoy anyways!!!!
